snippet.title: Ultra Hat Dimension: Official Trailer (2020)
snippet.description:
Ultra Hat Dimension is a puzzle game about adorable hats and people getting punched for wearing them. Available on Steam, Switch, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One.

itch.io: https://eniko.itch.io/uhd
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/628830/Ultra_Hat_Dimension/
Switch, PS4, Xbox One: https://www.ratalaikagames.com/games/ultrahatdimension.php#switch
